{"tid":817840,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"涉揸胸掃腰非禮女同事　男救生員被控9罪","createTime":"2018-09-13T15:41:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-14T00:54:25.000Z","uid":28366,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"f2fc7acba94895d67f0c7a63ec36529f5c45777a","tid":817840,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T15:41:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/13/234103_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F13%2F234103_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=866520b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在黃大仙私人屋苑泳池任職的男救生員，於前年5月當值期間，涉在8日內共十多次胸襲和掃腰非禮女同事，其中3次更疑伸手入女同事的胸圍內犯案，事主稱因怕患癌症的父母擔心而啞忍，最終向風雨蘭求助後決定報警。現年22歲男救生員事後否認9項非禮罪，案件今(13日)在九龍城法院受審。 <br />\n<br />\n大專畢業的女事主X(21歲)供稱，她於前年5月1日至18日在上述屋苑擔任兼職救生員，當中8日她和被告魏家俊一同當值。她指當值期間都會和被告坐在櫈上玩手機或談話，被告在案發時段內，曾19次趁沒有其他人在場時，突然出手揸她的右胸，每次她都罵被告：「妖！唔好搞我！」但被告不但不道歉，更露出猥瑣笑容。此外，有一次她和被告清潔泳池時，被告突行到其身後，用手從她右腰掃向左，她即時行開瞪着被告，並發出「唧」一聲表示不滿。 <br />\n<br />\nX表示父母均有癌症，案發前曾接受手術，擔心自己報警後會驚動父母，令父母受刺激，但她最終和上司和朋友商量後，得悉年滿18歲，報警亦可以不讓家人知道，加上向風雨蘭求助後，最終於前年6月決定報警。 <br />\n<br />\n辯方盤問X時質疑，她在事發後有否想過不和被告一起坐，或在兩人之間放更多櫈以隔開被告。她承認有想過，但沒有付諸實行，指會所規定救生員必須坐在案發的椅子，即使夠位在兩人中間多放一張椅子，但被告仍能夠伸手碰其胸部。她表示因怕被告報復，故一直沒有向上司匯報事件，直至被告於6月中因欲投考康文署救生員而離職後，才敢向上司說出事件。 <br />\n<br />\n辯方又質疑，X在書面供詞中，提及遭被告非禮的次數，與庭上證供不符。她同意，解釋稱遭非禮的次數太多，難以清晰回答遭非禮多少次。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180913/mobile/bkn-20180913133757690-0913_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180913%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20180913133757690-0913_00822_001.html&d=ft9ksCca5MMv8Buqu4KpWcVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=5a7332e4\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180913/mobile/bkn-20180913133757690-0913_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"4a1faf28f3e3edaa21d598e1c14eeef818945da7","tid":817840,"uid":24045,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T18:03:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 正正經經溝條女先揸啦"},{"pid":"816e6b145eef6329191f96a33ac59ed821458827","tid":817840,"uid":12404,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T18:05:24.000Z","msg":"快點非禮我<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"476a2e3f957f186027b2384c503b9e3d7ef1e59a","tid":817840,"uid":209487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T18:11:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0226cb2cd12156d3a41e6f94f1e54f9f490449dd","tid":817840,"uid":155253,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T18:14:46.000Z","msg":"冇證據真係睇個官信邊個<br />\n條女係唔係9吹根本冇人知"},{"pid":"664afe8df57353efe3c4d9ee6d7f26d6966b9a47","tid":817840,"uid":120070,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T19:05:55.000Z","msg":"原來伸哂手入bra都只叫非禮<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70baa702a75f2875b46640f0ecbbf3dc6a461d05","tid":817840,"uid":130365,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T19:21:39.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">勞</span></span>"},{"pid":"8e67e5816ef6f8f324a9337be39a5b495913bfa9","tid":817840,"uid":27664,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T19:22:58.000Z","msg":"可以揸女同事波揸到自己轉工先唔再揸，真係正 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"859eca85fb4096d4710ec8ab8d01b957e834619c","tid":817840,"uid":120070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8e67e5816ef6f8f324a9337be39a5b495913bfa9","tid":817840,"uid":27664,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T19:22:58.000Z","msg":"可以揸女同事波揸到自己轉工先唔再揸，真係正 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T19:30:14.000Z","msg":"亦是無負這一生 無悔啦有份咁嘅工！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n返工揸波幾多打工仔夢想 好多港豬一世都冇咁既機會<br />\n成就達成啦"},{"pid":"c8263de0fce3e17dfa24df217717ad8d93164fff","tid":817840,"uid":22535,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"664afe8df57353efe3c4d9ee6d7f26d6966b9a47","tid":817840,"uid":120070,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T19:05:55.000Z","msg":"原來伸哂手入bra都只叫非禮<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T20:09:55.000Z","msg":"唔係叫咩，強姦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64d2a19c3bacddc07d6f29c7044e68ada6dc212d","tid":817840,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T00:08:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e2b623052c93ff60b3a72e160733df975af04b3","tid":817840,"uid":67500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T00:54:25.000Z","msg":"玩完，口罩都唔戴"}]}